July 5, 2017, Tim reported directly to Joe

I can say, without hesitation, Joe Arnone was one of the best people I have ever reported to in my professional career.  He has a very solid software development background and he strives to create an environment that any software developer could appreciate.  As the Vice President of Product Development at OpenTech Alliance,  Joe shielded the development team from the sometimes chaotic environment of the rest of the company.  Joe encouraged the company to move to a larger open environment for the development team.  Joe took the time to speak with each member of the development team to find out what their needs were and how they could be more productive.  Joe often provided encouragement and constructive feedback to team members in a positive way.Joe also has a unique background from his own startup experience which provides the team with a balanced perspective of engineering and business needs.  Joe's personal style of communication and his personality make it easy to trust him and he's able to motivate the team in a very genuine manner.  I would gladly work for him again.
